Guarnire con arancia e fragola.',NULL,NULL,'https://www.thecocktaildb.com/images/media/drink/szmj2d1504889961.jpg','Vodka','Creme de Banane','Grenadine','Orange juice',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2 cl','2 cl',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'No','2017-09-08 17:59:21');
